  "text": "Fly strains were grown at 258C in standard Drosophila medium. The following stocks were used: Canton-S. polo 1 /TM6C. w; polo 9 /TM6C. w; polo [CITATION_1] /TM6C. Immunostaining of testes and third instar larval neuroblasts was performed as described previously [CITATION_2] . For drug treatment, larval neuroblasts were dissected and treated with either dimethylsulfoxide (DMSO) or 100 nM BI 2536 for 2 h before being processed for immunostaining as described previously [CITATION_3] . ",
